title: Idle Dino Farm Tycoon 3D
description: Idle Dino Farm Tycoon 3D is a casual tycoon game where you helm a prehistoric spectacle, nurturing dinosaurs from hatchlings to colossal wonders. As the park's new manager, your goal is to expand, enthrall visitors, and unveil unique hybrid dinosaurs. Construct habitats, amass funds from intrigued spectators, and elevate your park's status. With each decision, you shape the ultimate Jurassic World experience, featuring awe-inspiring reptiles that capture the imagination of all who visit!
